Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.30,0:00:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惊爆危机\NFULL METAL PANIC
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.34,0:00:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两人一起寻找逃避之处
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在太阳雨中奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.09,0:00:39.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使会失去什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.73,0:00:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯有一件事 一定要去保护
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.27,0:00:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诞生于这个世界的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.75,0:01:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与你一起去寻找
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.29,0:01:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使拥抱着痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.69,0:01:13.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去迎接新的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.95,0:01:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,#12 ONE NlGHT STAND
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.66,0:01:44.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:01:56.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加里宁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.41,0:01:59.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算世界灭亡了\n那大叔也不会死的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:05.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是陆上自卫队的96式
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.58,0:02:40.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.52,0:02:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.42,0:02:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.73,0:02:47.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.79,0:02:50.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅莉莎\n用单分子切割刀瞄准姆指
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.93,0:02:52.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在正…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.57,0:03:03.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.36,0:03:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,λ-Driver，B机能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.73,0:03:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧，来试看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.21,0:03:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.41,0:03:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错，就是盾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,λ-Driver
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.39,0:03:52.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.02,0:04:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.79,0:04:24.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没有发现到我对你的好感
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.22,0:04:26.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迟钝的泰斯塔罗莎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.89,0:04:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我如果在那个时候\n杀了琢磨的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.93,0:04:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人就会放弃启动那架贝希摩斯(Behemoth)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.80,0:04:39.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.11,0:04:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:46.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然得不到，那就摧毁掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.42,0:04:52.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.95,0:04:54.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰莎，坐上去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.32,0:04:55.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来推，宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.26,0:04:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你驾驶了，宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.02,0:05:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上校大人，上校大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上校大人，增援呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:46.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得想办法解决那个巨人才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:48.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请下指令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.48,0:05:53.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人能逃得出我的手掌心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.78,0:05:56.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人能够阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:12.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长，真高兴您没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.27,0:06:18.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马德加斯，现在潜舰来到哪里了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.90,0:06:22.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纪伊半岛南方120公里附近
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.07,0:06:23.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太远了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.24,0:06:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧急配置的喷射器也在射程外\n(AS射出用装置)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.91,0:06:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上校大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.08,0:06:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用弹道飞弹把强弩兵(Arbalest)送过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.81,0:06:29.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备时间最少也要花一个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.09,0:06:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在送达前的这一两个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个巨人贝希摩斯(Behemoth)不知道\n会给这城市带来多大的损害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.26,0:06:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没办法，我已经无计可施了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长，现在的情势\n需要强弩兵(Arbalest)吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.64,0:06:50.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在立刻吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.54,0:06:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就发射吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:57.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:06:59.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然没有得到您许可
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.68,0:07:05.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是载有强弩兵(Arbalest)的弹道飞弹\n已经准备好可在3分钟内发射
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.22,0:07:08.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射后约6分钟\n大概就能抵达那里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:11.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说\n需要花费9分钟的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.46,0:07:14.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马德加斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.13,0:07:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已有觉悟接受处罚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.86,0:07:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，你做得太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻发射
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:23.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是，舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,降落地点呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.14,0:07:27.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.24,0:07:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,降落后可能会随即遭到巨人攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:32.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要更复杂的地形
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.98,0:07:37.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,着陆后能够争取出数十秒的时间\n让驾驶可以过去搭乘的场所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,视野不要太辽阔比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.82,0:07:41.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是不能在闹区
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.45,0:07:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会把平民卷进来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.12,0:07:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照明较暗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.42,0:07:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且是限定的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.99,0:07:50.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且最好也能有高低差
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:51.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最适合的场所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.56,0:07:55.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够充分发挥\n强弩兵(Arbalest)能力的场所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.34,0:08:00.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.44,0:08:02.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.69,0:08:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:20.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它要开火了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.09,0:08:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到我叫你就转向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:21.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.99,0:08:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了，来了，来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:25.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:30.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果它再瞄准一点打过来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种小货车可是撑不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.87,0:08:33.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗介，让车子一直线向前跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.84,0:08:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给那家伙一点颜色瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.51,0:08:38.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了吗，绝对要一直线喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.61,0:08:40.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,速度也不要改变
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:41.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.52,0:08:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想干嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:49.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安静点，小要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就会知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.79,0:08:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧，瞄准我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.40,0:08:57.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.47,0:09:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右头部火神炮损毁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我的贝希摩斯(Behemoth)…\N诱爆回避完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右头部火神炮无法使用\N竟敢伤了它…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.25,0:09:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克鲁兹好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼，交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:24.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为你只是个\n光说不练的软弱家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.82,0:09:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要安心还太早
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.46,0:10:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝希摩斯(Behemoth)…启动了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.77,0:10:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯，你赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经都无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:22.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要破坏它是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.48,0:10:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燃料可以撑40个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:27.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前，没人能够阻止它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就要看琢磨了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:33.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得对不起他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为记忆混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.06,0:10:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知何时竟把我当成\n被他亲手杀死的姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.67,0:10:44.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就凭着这点利用了他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.50,0:10:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本就没有亲人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.24,0:10:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直…都是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不问我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:10:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.62,0:10:59.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救你的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.25,0:11:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猜得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.29,0:11:04.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那种好像什么都知道的口气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.82,0:11:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真令人厌恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直让人想吐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.30,0:11:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最讨厌的你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以告诉我你的名字吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安德鲁·赛格维奇·加里宁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.51,0:11:28.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:56.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的，还以为死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.68,0:12:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认识的人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:04.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.49,0:12:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲吧，冲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时间笑的话就再开一枪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.13,0:12:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说傻话了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.06,0:12:19.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样动来动去怎么射
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.60,0:12:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.44,0:12:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.84,0:12:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个，之前也有看过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.41,0:12:32.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了，被看得清清楚楚的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.96,0:12:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.93,0:12:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，还没
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那架机体不会这么简单就坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相良
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.53,0:12:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.30,0:12:55.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.64,0:12:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是高中生耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.31,0:13:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的，让我来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.47,0:13:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转弯，小要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以煞车
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:08.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下来就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的，会怎样我可不管喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.45,0:13:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野牛6号呼叫野牛7号
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.46,0:13:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是野牛7号
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:22.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在拖拖拉拉个什么劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.13,0:13:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手动操纵杆被压在地板
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法强制分割容器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.93,0:13:30.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法打破蛋壳是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.44,0:13:33.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.24,0:13:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.31,0:13:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果变成炒蛋的话\n就都是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.14,0:13:38.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要诅咒你\n直到你的子孙十八代
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.11,0:13:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有最后一枚手榴弹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.44,0:13:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用这试看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加速
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.03,0:13:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.77,0:14:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面，里面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.93,0:14:03.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲破铁卷门进去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:16.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰莎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:20.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.05,0:14:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前也有过这种…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.52,0:14:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点逃吧，小要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.43,0:14:37.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,λ-Driver，A机能低落
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:40.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骨骼系发生干扰波
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.24,0:14:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，得集中精神才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相良宗介在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道啦，笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:48.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会去问你姊姊吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.51,0:14:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找我有事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.56,0:15:01.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在猎物面前舔舌头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是三流的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.66,0:15:04.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.86,0:15:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来当你的对手，过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.40,0:15:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行不通吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:30.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.96,0:15:34.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？小要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.73,0:15:43.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样才能…好冰…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:45.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷…冷却？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小要，拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:50.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你告诉他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.44,0:15:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用λ-Driver
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.94,0:15:54.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把巨人的其中一个冷却装置…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:55.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:15:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,R
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.68,0:16:01.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,YES，士官
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.52,0:16:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这架机体有搭载λ-Driver
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.96,0:16:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:07.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假设敌机有搭载λ-Driver
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可以对抗它的手段吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.16,0:16:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.43,0:16:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以现场士官的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:17.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要求提供情报
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.84,0:16:19.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受要求
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.50,0:16:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.28,0:16:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.31,0:16:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把意识…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.86,0:16:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右膝盖连接部损伤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.66,0:16:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗介，听得到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:49.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千鸟吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:52.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…仔细听好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.34,0:16:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我搞不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.81,0:16:57.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过脚的连结部分好像有\nλ-Driver的冷却装置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:16:59.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.31,0:17:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻击那个地方，大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.21,0:17:03.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.21,0:17:04.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只知道这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.98,0:17:06.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且不能用普通的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.68,0:17:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要用λ-Driver
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.15,0:17:09.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那上面有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是上校大人说的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说泰莎吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.29,0:17:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…大概是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.69,0:17:15.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就当作是那样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.89,0:17:17.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的回答怎么这么随便…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.56,0:17:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.27,0:17:25.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要慌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不要觉得很无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.94,0:17:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接下来所要发射的子弹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:33.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将会贯穿它的盾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.85,0:17:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要这么的相信才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.35,0:17:38.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错，就像那个时候一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.35,0:17:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一条细长的隙缝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.59,0:17:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左右哪边都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.26,0:17:49.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中意识
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.66,0:17:52.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会中…一定要打中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.73,0:17:53.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破坏它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.40,0:17:55.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.08,0:18:08.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,λ-Driver机能停止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.91,0:18:10.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有回复的余地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.85,0:18:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝希摩斯(Behemoth)因重量过重开始分解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.65,0:18:50.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我输了，姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:51.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.62,0:18:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你并没有输
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.29,0:18:55.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是这种事有时也会发生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:57.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样子太过份了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:19:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错，的确很过份
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.03,0:19:04.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经什么都没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系，琢磨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.97,0:19:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.47,0:19:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会一直陪在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.11,0:19:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.68,0:19:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯，安心的入睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.98,0:19:21.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯，对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.80,0:19:36.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了，威巴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.93,0:19:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的技术还是一样的棒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.27,0:19:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯，还好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:42.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了，相良
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:44.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里，上校大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.48,0:19:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这架机体已经是你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.65,0:19:49.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你好好珍惜它喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:51.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.15,0:19:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有…小要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:56.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要特别感谢你才行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:19:58.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你真这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:20:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能好好说明一下这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.39,0:20:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯，改天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.29,0:20:03.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.16,0:20:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我也很累了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.06,0:20:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过，我能跟你宣言一件事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宣言？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相良士官\n把听觉感应器全部关掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.84,0:20:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.64,0:20:18.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了…了解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.84,0:20:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像喜欢上他了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那个…我…\n泰莎，泰莎…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.69,0:20:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我还是跟你说一声\n“我们互相加油吧”好了，小要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.96,0:20:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.16,0:20:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰莎的春天到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.66,0:20:41.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰莎的春天到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.17,0:20:43.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚吃红豆饭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.20,0:20:46.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加里宁他们似乎平安无事喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:24.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在心中绽开着一朵小花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.54,0:21:36.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我的那朵不会枯萎的花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:42.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我不再畏惧相信他人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:49.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得更坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.33,0:21:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能与你相遇 真的很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.94,0:22:02.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能与你牵手 是我的骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.58,0:22:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使现在各自仰望着不同的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.32,0:22:17.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 我一个人仍能向前迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.74,0:22:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请听我说，梅莉莎竟然看不起我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.58,0:22:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是泰莎你自己先找我麻烦的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.58,0:22:38.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能原谅，我要跟你决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.32,0:22:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好，我会好好疼你的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.65,0:22:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一回 FULL METAL PANIC\n「猫与小猫的R&R(ROCK AND ROLL)」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.86,0:22:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好担心
